text: This was the first edition of the event as a WTA International tournament. Raquel Kops-Jones and Abigail Spears won the title, defeating Jocelyn Rae and Anna Smith in the final, 3–6, 6–3, [11–9]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== == References == * Main draw Aegon Open Nottingham - Doubles Category:Nottingham Open
